title: BRIEF-Diana Shipping Announces Time Charter Contract For M/V Melia With United

organizations.name: united reuters staff    diana shipping inc

text:
April 10, 2018 / 12:57 PM / Updated 6 minutes ago BRIEF-Diana Shipping Announces Time Charter Contract For M/V Melia With United Reuters Staff 
April 10 (Reuters) - Diana Shipping Inc: 
* . ANNOUNCES TIME CHARTER CONTRACT FOR M/V MELIA WITH UNITED 
* EMPLOYMENT IS ANTICIPATED TO GENERATE APPROXIMATELY US$6.12 MILLION OF GROSS REVENUE FOR MINIMUM SCHEDULED PERIOD OF TIME CHARTER 
* GROSS CHARTER RATE IS $12,000/DAY, MINUS A 5% COMMISSION PAID TO THIRD PARTIES, FOR A MINIMUM 17 MONTHS TO MAXIMUM 20 MONTHS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
